reviews.title: Does not work on big TV!
reviews.comment: Bought this app for my boy. Bought a HD media link in order to play on the big TV. And guess what? It does not show! Only the main screen works. There is only sound but no video! Now my boy cant enjoy the show without stressing his eyes on the phone!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Nice idea ...but
reviews.comment: First the positives: Large collection of rhymes  Above average quality sound   Negatives: Have to download each set separately which is a pain For an app that charges 5$ I expected a better quality of animation - not just 2 kids dancing. That becomes stale pretty soon. My 3 year old daughter lost interest after 2-3 songs.
